- 317     : 2. **Standalone config filename** — The standalone config file at the project root needs a well-known name. Candidates: `.sandpiper-tasks.json`, `sandpiper-tasks.config.json`, `.tasks.json`. Leaning toward `.sandpiper-tasks.json` for namespace clarity.
